I"j<p>Elemontary OSâ€™s default terminal is <code class="highlighter-rouge">Pantheon terminal</code>. <br />
With this terminal, its quite hard to change settings.
So I decided to replace the pantheon with the <code class="highlighter-rouge">GNOME terminal</code>.</p>

